567
00:22:06,540 --> 00:22:07,270
This won't work.

568
00:22:07,710 --> 00:22:08,950
Madam, you see,

569
00:22:09,060 --> 00:22:10,060
when the townies are here,

570
00:22:10,140 --> 00:22:12,430
those simple country dishes are all they want.

571
00:22:12,750 --> 00:22:14,710
We only need to work a little more
on the presentation.

572
00:22:14,710 --> 00:22:16,510
Don't worry. I'll take care of that.

573
00:22:18,380 --> 00:22:20,060
Really?

574
00:22:22,230 --> 00:22:22,580
Then...

