00:22:23,580 --> 00:22:24,670
Will I get paid?

576
00:22:25,140 --> 00:22:27,380
That's for sure. You can't be working for free.

577
00:22:27,910 --> 00:22:28,990
2,000 yuan a month.

578
00:22:29,060 --> 00:22:30,140
You'll have to cook three meals a day.

579
00:22:30,270 --> 00:22:31,140
What do you think?

580
00:22:32,340 --> 00:22:34,060
You get pensions from the village too.

581
00:22:34,380 --> 00:22:36,100
Just consider this your pocket money.

582
00:22:37,470 --> 00:22:38,670
2,000 yuan...

583
00:22:39,190 --> 00:22:40,230
That's not a lot.

584
00:22:40,580 --> 00:22:41,750
Can you offer more?

585
00:22:43,270 --> 00:22:44,710
Your inn

586
00:22:44,750 --> 00:22:47,030
is so far from the village.

587
00:22:47,030 --> 00:22:49,430
I'm too old to be traveling that much daily.

588
00:22:50,540 --> 00:22:51,380
Madam.

589
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:52,470
You saw it yourself.

590
00:22:52,580 --> 00:22:54,270
I only started operating this inn not long ago.

591
00:22:54,820 --> 00:22:55,860
I'm not earning much.

592
00:22:56,470 --> 00:22:59,100
All my expenses still depend on crowdfunding.

593
00:22:59,580 --> 00:23:01,140
I'm a little tight on money.

594
00:23:01,750 --> 00:23:03,030
Everyone has been showing me great support,

595
00:23:03,030 --> 00:23:04,380
and I don't want to let them down.

596
00:23:04,990 --> 00:23:07,910
I'm only trying to save as much as I can now.

597
00:23:08,820 --> 00:23:09,710
Don't worry.

598
00:23:10,510 --> 00:23:13,100
When I manage to keep the business on track,

599
00:23:13,100 --> 00:23:14,470
I'll definitely give you a raise.

600
00:23:16,780 --> 00:23:17,580
Xingfu.

601
00:23:19,990 --> 00:23:20,780
Xiuyu.

602
00:23:20,780 --> 00:23:21,710
Madam, you're here.

603
00:23:22,990 --> 00:23:25,060
You're getting prettier and prettier.

604
00:23:25,950 --> 00:23:27,540
Don't you work for the Group?

605
00:23:27,540 --> 00:23:28,950
Why are you helping out at the inn too?

606
00:23:28,950 --> 00:23:30,470
I invested some money too

607
00:23:30,470 --> 00:23:31,780
and am considered a minority shareholder.

608
00:23:32,340 --> 00:23:32,990
Xingfu.

609
00:23:33,270 --> 00:23:35,140
Aren't you looking for someone who can cook?

610
00:23:35,910 --> 00:23:37,670
My colleague introduced someone to me.

611
00:23:37,710 --> 00:23:39,140
Why don't we meet her up?

612
00:23:39,910 --> 00:23:41,230
There's no need to keep looking.

613
00:23:41,780 --> 00:23:42,910
I'm right here.

614
00:23:43,100 --> 00:23:45,380
Xingfu and I were discussing this just now.

615
00:23:45,990 --> 00:23:47,270
When can I start?

616
00:23:47,910 --> 00:23:49,030
What about Friday?

617
00:23:49,030 --> 00:23:50,060
We have more guests on weekends.

618
00:23:50,860 --> 00:23:52,140
You can use the coming two days to get prepared.

619
00:23:52,380 --> 00:23:54,540
You can do a blood test and a check-up
at the hospital.

620
00:23:54,540 --> 00:23:55,470
I'll bear the cost.

621
00:23:56,270 --> 00:23:57,620
After all, we're chefs.

622
00:23:57,780 --> 00:23:59,710
We would like others
to enjoy the food with confidence.

623
00:23:59,860 --> 00:24:00,780
Sure.

624
00:24:01,470 --> 00:24:03,030
Having stayed in the city

625
00:24:03,100 --> 00:24:03,860
does make you different.

626
00:24:04,270 --> 00:24:06,100
I can rest assured too after the check-up.

627
00:24:06,380 --> 00:24:06,950
Sure.

628
00:24:08,100 --> 00:24:09,860
You should get back to work. I'll get going.

629
00:24:10,190 --> 00:24:10,820
Madam.

630
00:24:13,950 --> 00:24:15,540
Here's a menu for you.

631
00:24:15,540 --> 00:24:16,270
You can study it at home.

632
00:24:16,620 --> 00:24:18,190
I'm wondering if you can add

633
00:24:18,580 --> 00:24:20,140
a few signature dishes of yours to it.

634
00:24:21,030 --> 00:24:21,750
Of course.

635
00:24:21,780 --> 00:24:23,030
I'll study it later.

636
00:24:23,030 --> 00:24:24,470
-Sure. I'll consider the deal sealed.
-Okay.

637
00:24:24,950 --> 00:24:25,190
Madam.

638
00:24:25,190 --> 00:24:25,860
Sure.

639
00:24:26,100 --> 00:24:26,860
I'll get going.

640
00:24:27,140 --> 00:24:27,470
Sure.

641
00:24:27,470 --> 00:24:28,190
I've got to go.

642
00:24:29,190 --> 00:24:30,060
Then...

643
00:24:30,060 --> 00:24:31,380
I'll be here on Friday.

644
00:24:31,510 --> 00:24:32,190
Sure.

645
00:24:32,300 --> 00:24:33,060
Bye, Madam.

646
00:24:33,060 --> 00:24:34,030
Goodbye.

647
00:24:37,540 --> 00:24:39,300
Why did you insist on hiring her?

648
00:24:39,620 --> 00:24:40,300
What's wrong?

649
00:24:42,230 --> 00:24:43,820
I dislike her.

650
00:24:44,190 --> 00:24:44,990
Why?

651
00:24:47,710 --> 00:24:49,030
You can easily hire another cook.

652
00:24:49,140 --> 00:24:50,910
I can get you someone from the city.

653
00:24:51,380 --> 00:24:53,030
Every time there's a special occasion
in the village,

654
00:24:53,030 --> 00:24:54,340
everyone approaches her
and asks her to help prepare the food.

655
00:24:54,470 --> 00:24:55,820
She cooks really well.

656
00:24:55,910 --> 00:24:57,430
That's a taste you can only get in our village.

657
00:24:57,540 --> 00:24:59,270
The chefs from the city are different.

658
00:25:00,100 --> 00:25:01,510
This is for the greater good, okay?

659
00:25:02,470 --> 00:25:02,990
I...

660
00:25:03,510 --> 00:25:04,710
I dislike the old woman.

661
00:25:05,540 --> 00:25:06,380
I won't be in the same place as her.

662
00:25:12,030 --> 00:25:12,540
Hello.

663
00:25:12,540 --> 00:25:13,580
Xingfu Inn.

664
00:25:15,140 --> 00:25:16,910
Sorry. We don't need any of that.

665
00:25:17,540 --> 00:25:18,710
We don't need it. Thanks.

666
00:25:19,820 --> 00:25:20,580
Ms. He.

667
00:25:21,510 --> 00:25:23,140
Madam Qi, why are you here?

668
00:25:24,100 --> 00:25:25,030
I'm here to admit that I was wrong.

669
00:25:25,060 --> 00:25:26,190
And I'm here to fulfill my promise.

670
00:25:26,750 --> 00:25:28,100
Have you gotten the test results already?

671
00:25:28,710 --> 00:25:29,470
Did it pass the assessment?

672
00:25:29,710 --> 00:25:30,670
It didn't only pass the assessment,

673
00:25:30,670 --> 00:25:32,270
but it's also way above the standard.

674
00:25:33,190 --> 00:25:34,380
Above the standard?

675
00:25:36,140 --> 00:25:36,710
From now on,

676
00:25:36,750 --> 00:25:38,300
this will be your inn's best selling point.

677
00:25:38,340 --> 00:25:39,140
I suggest you

678
00:25:39,140 --> 00:25:40,750
frame this page

679
00:25:40,780 --> 00:25:42,340
that comes with the parameters.

680
00:25:42,540 --> 00:25:43,470
Those who know

681
00:25:43,540 --> 00:25:44,670
will be able to tell how good it is at a glance.

682
00:25:45,540 --> 00:25:46,710
Sure.

683
00:25:46,910 --> 00:25:48,100
Thanks, Madam Qi.

684
00:25:48,230 --> 00:25:48,510
See?

685
00:25:48,510 --> 00:25:50,190
I told you the water wasn't bad.

686
00:25:51,190 --> 00:25:52,340
Yes, you were totally right.

687
00:25:52,340 --> 00:25:54,030
In fact, it's really good.

688
00:25:54,340 --> 00:25:55,300
I forgot to introduce him to you.

689
00:25:55,430 --> 00:25:56,820
This is my husband.

690
00:25:57,820 --> 00:25:59,190
I promised

691
00:25:59,270 --> 00:26:00,380
that I would introduce customers to you.

692
00:26:00,470 --> 00:26:01,580
His company

693
00:26:01,990 --> 00:26:03,230
organizes a lot of events.

694
00:26:03,270 --> 00:26:04,860
For instance, team-building,

695
00:26:04,860 --> 00:26:06,230
client meetings,

696
00:26:06,540 --> 00:26:08,060
seminars, and so on.

697
00:26:08,230 --> 00:26:09,670
The only trouble they have
is not getting the perfect place.

698
00:26:09,750 --> 00:26:10,750
I introduced your inn

699
00:26:10,750 --> 00:26:11,670
to him,

700
00:26:11,670 --> 00:26:12,910
and he said he wanted to come and take a look.

701
00:26:13,950 --> 00:26:14,780
Welcome.

702
00:26:15,580 --> 00:26:16,100
Ms. He.

703
00:26:16,100 --> 00:26:16,750
It's nice to meet you.

704
00:26:16,860 --> 00:26:17,860
Nice meeting you too.

705
00:26:23,670 --> 00:26:26,300
It would be great if Qingzhi could proceed
with his wedding.

706
00:26:27,430 --> 00:26:28,780
It should be done as soon as possible.

707
00:26:29,030 --> 00:26:30,030
Qingzhi's wedding

708
00:26:30,430 --> 00:26:32,140
will be another major event for our family.

709
00:26:33,270 --> 00:26:34,950
Qingzhi's father-in-law

710
00:26:35,430 --> 00:26:37,030
is a reputable man.

711
00:26:38,340 --> 00:26:40,140
We can't save on our dowry.

712
00:26:40,750 --> 00:26:42,190
We also need a grand wedding.

713
00:26:42,430 --> 00:26:44,380
We need his father-in-law

714
00:26:44,380 --> 00:26:45,470
to take care of Qingzhi in the future.

715
00:26:46,820 --> 00:26:48,100
According to Qinglai,

716
00:26:49,270 --> 00:26:50,230
Qingzhi hasn't met

717
00:26:50,230 --> 00:26:51,950
his mother-in-law's standard yet.

718
00:26:53,710 --> 00:26:54,470
That's why

719
00:26:54,510 --> 00:26:57,030
we must not be stingy.

720
00:26:57,190 --> 00:26:59,340
Didn't they say they didn't want any dowry?

721
00:27:00,470 --> 00:27:01,820
They were just saying.

722
00:27:02,140 --> 00:27:03,100
Even if they don't want any dowry,

723
00:27:03,100 --> 00:27:04,470
we still need to do a grand wedding.

724
00:27:04,710 --> 00:27:05,750
I have asked around.

725
00:27:05,750 --> 00:27:07,100
It takes hundreds of thousands of yuan

726
00:27:07,140 --> 00:27:08,950
to organize a wedding in the city.

727
00:27:09,670 --> 00:27:10,270
What?

728
00:27:10,580 --> 00:27:11,710
Why is it so expensive?

729
00:27:12,470 --> 00:27:13,430
If I have that much money,

730
00:27:13,670 --> 00:27:14,990
why don't I use it to live a good life?

731
00:27:15,100 --> 00:27:16,060
That's ridiculous.

732
00:27:16,430 --> 00:27:17,270
What do you suggest we do, then?

733
00:27:17,470 --> 00:27:19,860
It's a competition between families.

734
00:27:20,470 --> 00:27:23,140
Some even borrow money just to save faces.

735
00:27:24,190 --> 00:27:25,100
Tell you what.

736
00:27:25,710 --> 00:27:26,990
The two of us

737
00:27:27,230 --> 00:27:28,430
have been working really hard

738
00:27:28,950 --> 00:27:29,990
to save some money,

739
00:27:30,990 --> 00:27:32,060
but it's still far from enough.

740
00:27:32,860 --> 00:27:34,030
What should we do then?

741
00:27:39,910 --> 00:27:40,430
Mom.

742
00:27:41,030 --> 00:27:42,190
Do we still have eggs at home?

743
00:27:42,950 --> 00:27:43,910
We still have a few.

744
00:27:44,380 --> 00:27:45,380
Just a few?

745
00:27:45,380 --> 00:27:47,060
Didn't you already bring them to the inn?

746
00:27:47,100 --> 00:27:47,580
We're running out

747
00:27:47,580 --> 00:27:48,540
of eggs again.

748
00:27:49,510 --> 00:27:50,670
If you keep consuming the eggs like this,

749
00:27:50,670 --> 00:27:51,820
we won't be able to sustain.

750
00:27:52,750 --> 00:27:53,860
They are rushing me,

751
00:27:53,860 --> 00:27:55,380
telling me to get the eggs and vegetables.

752
00:27:55,710 --> 00:27:57,100
I'll have to head to the wet market then.

753
00:28:00,910 --> 00:28:01,860
Drive safe.

754
00:28:03,750 --> 00:28:04,620
Mr. Wan.

755
00:28:05,380 --> 00:28:06,670
I've sent someone to ask around.

756
00:28:08,140 --> 00:28:09,100
Mr. Xie

757
00:28:09,780 --> 00:28:10,990
is not short of cash.

758
00:28:11,910 --> 00:28:12,860
He simply wants to hold the goods

759
00:28:13,580 --> 00:28:14,820
and delay the payment.

760
00:28:15,780 --> 00:28:16,820
It's something he usually does.

761
00:28:17,750 --> 00:28:18,470
I got it.

762
00:28:18,580 --> 00:28:20,030
I've hired a lawyer.

763
00:28:20,750 --> 00:28:21,620
I'll first send him a letter of demand.

764
00:28:21,620 --> 00:28:22,470
If it still doesn't work,
I'll file a lawsuit against him.

765
00:28:24,030 --> 00:28:25,190
This guy

766
00:28:25,990 --> 00:28:26,990
has our products' distribution rights

767
00:28:26,990 --> 00:28:28,910
in all the five provinces of the South.

768
00:28:29,030 --> 00:28:30,030
If things get ugly between us,

769
00:28:30,140 --> 00:28:31,860
it will not only affect our sales performance,

770
00:28:32,100 --> 00:28:32,750
but we might also

771
00:28:33,780 --> 00:28:35,620
find it difficult to sell our products

772
00:28:36,030 --> 00:28:36,860
in these five provinces in the future.

773
00:28:36,860 --> 00:28:38,860
I'm desperate, Mo.

774
00:28:39,230 --> 00:28:40,750
I can't be bothered by the future.

775
00:28:42,430 --> 00:28:43,950
The market is not doing well right now.

776
00:28:44,380 --> 00:28:46,190
It's not an issue we can solve so easily.

777
00:28:46,710 --> 00:28:47,670
Tell my father that.

778
00:28:49,140 --> 00:28:50,340
You're telling me these,

779
00:28:50,340 --> 00:28:51,620
but do you think I dare say the same words to him?

780
00:28:52,750 --> 00:28:53,540
Stop laughing.

781
00:28:54,620 --> 00:28:55,910
Everything he said the last time

782
00:28:55,910 --> 00:28:57,380
was aimed at me.

783
00:28:58,190 --> 00:28:59,540
From the very beginning,

784
00:28:59,860 --> 00:29:02,190
I've been in charge of
the Health Products Factory.

785
00:29:02,620 --> 00:29:04,190
Now that we're at a sales plateau,

786
00:29:04,190 --> 00:29:05,030
we have run into problems.

787
00:29:05,540 --> 00:29:06,340
Of course,

788
00:29:06,710 --> 00:29:07,910
he wants to throw

789
00:29:08,710 --> 00:29:10,030
all the problems at me.

790
00:29:11,100 --> 00:29:12,380
He won't be that mean, right?

791
00:29:12,620 --> 00:29:14,620
After all, he's your dad.

792
00:29:14,620 --> 00:29:15,750
He won't act so unreasonably, right?

793
00:29:15,750 --> 00:29:17,140
That's not funny.

794
00:29:18,820 --> 00:29:21,430
If there's anything that affects

795
00:29:21,950 --> 00:29:22,780
the results of the selection,

796
00:29:23,340 --> 00:29:25,430
he won't even bother being reasonable with me.

797
00:29:26,580 --> 00:29:28,580
He's my dad and I know him the best.

798
00:29:29,270 --> 00:29:30,300
For the past years,

799
00:29:30,300 --> 00:29:31,820
all he has cared about the most

800
00:29:32,060 --> 00:29:34,100
are those useless titles.

801
00:29:34,430 --> 00:29:36,270
He would rather give his son up

802
00:29:36,670 --> 00:29:38,780
than give those titles up.

803
00:29:39,300 --> 00:29:40,060
Then tell me.

804
00:29:40,540 --> 00:29:41,270
What do you mean?

805
00:29:41,620 --> 00:29:42,060
Wait, Mo.

806
00:29:42,060 --> 00:29:44,100
We've been talking for so long.

807
00:29:44,780 --> 00:29:45,710
What do you think I mean?

808
00:29:45,710 --> 00:29:46,540
You.

809
00:29:46,750 --> 00:29:47,750
I don't care whatever you do.

810
00:29:47,750 --> 00:29:49,780
You need to collect the outstanding payments

811
00:29:49,780 --> 00:29:51,190
as soon as possible.

812
00:29:52,340 --> 00:29:53,100
Come in.

813
00:29:55,230 --> 00:29:56,100
Ms. He.

814
00:29:56,580 --> 00:29:57,510
Mr. Mo.

815
00:29:58,060 --> 00:29:59,430
I'll leave you guys to have a chat.

816
00:29:59,430 --> 00:30:00,580
Get it done as soon as possible.

817
00:30:00,580 --> 00:30:01,340
I got it.

818
00:30:02,820 --> 00:30:03,470
Have a seat.

819
00:30:15,300 --> 00:30:15,780
Xingyun.

820
00:30:16,380 --> 00:30:17,380
I asked you here

821
00:30:17,580 --> 00:30:19,510
because I want to ask you for a favor.

822
00:30:20,230 --> 00:30:21,580
Let me repeat this again.

823
00:30:21,860 --> 00:30:23,100
Call me Ms. He.

824
00:30:24,430 --> 00:30:25,380
Oh, come on.

825
00:30:25,710 --> 00:30:27,140
There's no need to put on an act
when you're with me.

826
00:30:27,140 --> 00:30:28,270
We're not strangers.

827
00:30:28,780 --> 00:30:29,950
Yes, we are.

828
00:30:30,710 --> 00:30:31,510
How can I help you?

829
00:30:32,300 --> 00:30:33,270
Cut straight to the chase,

830
00:30:34,670 --> 00:30:35,580
or I'll get going.

831
00:30:36,190 --> 00:30:36,670
Hey.

832
00:30:36,860 --> 00:30:38,820
Why are you in a hurry to leave?

833
00:30:38,820 --> 00:30:39,300
Have a seat.

834
00:30:40,340 --> 00:30:41,190
Have a seat and we can talk.

835
00:30:47,230 --> 00:30:48,430
Look at your temper.

836
00:30:48,750 --> 00:30:49,780
I try my best not to embarrass you

837
00:30:49,780 --> 00:30:51,230
when others are around.

838
00:30:51,710 --> 00:30:53,190
Now that you're in my office,

839
00:30:53,190 --> 00:30:54,100
behind a closed door,

840
00:30:54,270 --> 00:30:55,100
can't you just show me

841
00:30:55,430 --> 00:30:56,750
a little respect?

842
00:30:57,950 --> 00:31:00,230
After all, I spent money hiring you.

843
00:31:00,620 --> 00:31:02,430
Don't you consider me your God?

844
00:31:03,380 --> 00:31:04,620
Fine.

845
00:31:04,620 --> 00:31:05,300
What about this?

846
00:31:05,620 --> 00:31:07,910
Help me book two rooms

847
00:31:07,910 --> 00:31:08,910
at Xingfu Inn.

848
00:31:08,990 --> 00:31:10,670
I'm having a meeting with a very important client.

849
00:31:12,230 --> 00:31:13,340
What's wrong with you?

850
00:31:13,510 --> 00:31:14,950
Do you consider this an important matter?

851
00:31:15,270 --> 00:31:17,380
You can get one of your secretaries

852
00:31:17,380 --> 00:31:18,510
to give them a call.

853
00:31:18,860 --> 00:31:21,060
Do you really need to ask me
to come here from the city?

854
00:31:21,710 --> 00:31:22,620
Calm down.

855
00:31:23,190 --> 00:31:24,860
I called you here

856
00:31:25,140 --> 00:31:26,670
because I intended to hire you as my attorney.

857
00:31:27,060 --> 00:31:29,230
But I changed my mind at the eleventh hour.

858
00:31:29,230 --> 00:31:31,270
I want to be as polite as I can.

859
00:31:31,750 --> 00:31:32,430
I don't get it.

860
00:31:33,750 --> 00:31:35,670
Make it clear.

861
00:31:36,190 --> 00:31:36,910
This is what happened.

862
00:31:36,990 --> 00:31:37,990
There's a client

863
00:31:38,190 --> 00:31:39,190
of ours

864
00:31:39,190 --> 00:31:41,030
who still has a lot of outstanding balance to pay.

865
00:31:41,190 --> 00:31:42,100
I'm thinking

866
00:31:42,100 --> 00:31:43,580
maybe you can have a meal with the client.

867
00:31:43,820 --> 00:31:44,430
Then...

868
00:31:48,580 --> 00:31:49,670
Dream on.

869
00:31:50,230 --> 00:31:51,910
I'm not your sales representative.

870
00:31:52,470 --> 00:31:53,190
What's on your mind?

871
00:31:53,190 --> 00:31:54,710
Ms. He.

872
00:31:54,710 --> 00:31:55,540
Listen to me.

873
00:31:56,510 --> 00:31:57,470
There's a misunderstanding.

874
00:31:57,470 --> 00:31:58,780
We are a big group.

875
00:31:58,780 --> 00:32:00,580
Of course, we have
our own sales representatives, right?

876
00:32:01,030 --> 00:32:02,100
Moreover,

877
00:32:02,340 --> 00:32:03,950
I will never tell you

878
00:32:03,950 --> 00:32:05,670
to entertain my clients.

879
00:32:06,540 --> 00:32:07,710
You've misunderstood me.

880
00:32:07,910 --> 00:32:09,030
I want you

881
00:32:09,470 --> 00:32:10,510
to be my attorney.

882
00:32:10,820 --> 00:32:12,340
I want you to be there
when I talk to my client over the meal.

883
00:32:12,340 --> 00:32:14,030
That's just a statement from me, alright?

884
00:32:14,060 --> 00:32:16,780
Why are you always being stubborn
when others are being nice?

885
00:32:17,030 --> 00:32:18,470
Didn't you say it yourself?

886
00:32:18,780 --> 00:32:20,510
You know that I'm an attorney,

887
00:32:20,670 --> 00:32:22,100
not your staff.

888
00:32:22,670 --> 00:32:23,710
At most,

889
00:32:23,710 --> 00:32:25,510
we're just an agent and a client.

890
00:32:25,750 --> 00:32:27,580
Accompanying you to have a meal with your client

891
00:32:27,950 --> 00:32:29,540
is not part of my job description.

892
00:32:29,860 --> 00:32:31,750
You're right.

893
00:32:32,270 --> 00:32:33,140
Whatever you said

894
00:32:33,190 --> 00:32:34,140
makes perfect sense.

895
00:32:34,950 --> 00:32:36,030
However...

896
00:32:40,510 --> 00:32:41,100
Never mind.

897
00:32:48,540 --> 00:32:49,300
What?

898
00:32:51,300 --> 00:32:53,330
However, the agreement

899
00:32:53,330 --> 00:32:54,540
between your law firm

900
00:32:55,060 --> 00:32:56,060
and our group

901
00:32:56,090 --> 00:32:57,170
seems to be expiring soon.

902
00:32:58,700 --> 00:32:59,500
And?

903
00:33:00,410 --> 00:33:01,810
What does that have anything to do with me?

904
00:33:02,610 --> 00:33:04,780
It has everything to do with you.

905
00:33:05,410 --> 00:33:06,090
What are you trying to say?

906
00:33:07,740 --> 00:33:08,940
For these past years,

907
00:33:09,130 --> 00:33:11,460
I've come in touch

908
00:33:11,650 --> 00:33:12,940
with many different law firms.

909
00:33:13,650 --> 00:33:15,090
I have never seen

910
00:33:15,540 --> 00:33:16,500
a lawyer

911
00:33:16,700 --> 00:33:17,780
as young as Ms. He

912
00:33:17,980 --> 00:33:19,090
who gets to be

913
00:33:19,500 --> 00:33:20,850
the attorney of any large groups.

914
00:33:23,370 --> 00:33:25,610
There are many things you haven't seen before,

915
00:33:26,220 --> 00:33:27,300
but that doesn't mean
it has never happened before.

916
00:33:28,300 --> 00:33:30,370
Do you really want me to say it out loud?

917
00:33:30,370 --> 00:33:31,650
You owe everything you have today

918
00:33:31,650 --> 00:33:33,370
to the fact that you won
the legal representative rights of our group

919
00:33:33,370 --> 00:33:35,370
on behalf of your law firm.

920
00:33:35,850 --> 00:33:37,060
What are you trying to say?

921
00:33:37,650 --> 00:33:38,940
I'm only trying to tell you

922
00:33:39,330 --> 00:33:41,370
that this is a very simple task.

923
00:33:41,500 --> 00:33:42,060
You.

924
00:33:42,060 --> 00:33:42,850
Ms. He.

925
00:33:42,980 --> 00:33:43,780
I need you

926
00:33:43,780 --> 00:33:44,980
to help me get back this money

927
00:33:44,980 --> 00:33:46,370
because our group needs the money urgently.

928
00:33:46,370 --> 00:33:47,090
We need it to improve our sales performance.

929
00:33:47,570 --> 00:33:48,780
If you can do this,

930
00:33:49,090 --> 00:33:50,090
I'll renew the legal agreement

931
00:33:50,090 --> 00:33:51,890
between our group and your law firm.

932
00:33:52,410 --> 00:33:54,020
You can continue

933
00:33:54,020 --> 00:33:55,130
being Ms. He, the great lawyer.

934
00:33:59,890 --> 00:34:01,130
Look at what you have today.

935
00:34:01,650 --> 00:34:03,410
Do you really want

936
00:34:03,700 --> 00:34:05,260
to go back to being a trainee?

937
00:34:09,260 --> 00:34:10,300
Don't get mad.

938
00:34:11,610 --> 00:34:12,700
You're a girl.

939
00:34:13,090 --> 00:34:14,060
You shouldn't be angry all the time.

940
00:34:15,500 --> 00:34:16,330
Think about it.

941
00:34:41,090 --> 00:34:41,690
Hello.

942
00:34:41,690 --> 00:34:42,500
Where's Xingfu?

943
00:34:42,900 --> 00:34:43,770
She's away.

944
00:34:49,820 --> 00:34:50,420
Hey, Xingfu.

945
00:34:50,420 --> 00:34:51,250
Where are you?

946
00:34:51,770 --> 00:34:53,420
I'm at home sorting out the finances of the inn.

947
00:34:53,650 --> 00:34:54,650
I'll talk to you later.

948
00:34:55,060 --> 00:34:56,570
Xingfu, I need to talk to you.

949
00:34:56,570 --> 00:34:57,900
I'll see you at your place.

950
00:34:58,730 --> 00:34:59,340
See you later.

951
00:34:59,690 --> 00:35:00,210
Bye.

952
00:35:02,940 --> 00:35:03,980
You can just give me a call

953
00:35:03,980 --> 00:35:05,420
if you wish to book rooms.

954
00:35:05,820 --> 00:35:07,130
There's no need to come here personally.

955
00:35:07,650 --> 00:35:08,500
Who wants to book the room?

956
00:35:08,570 --> 00:35:09,540
Why did you go to this extent to help them?

957
00:35:10,460 --> 00:35:12,820
The southern distributor
of the Health Products Company.

958
00:35:13,170 --> 00:35:14,690
We're going to ask for the outstanding payments.

959
00:35:15,420 --> 00:35:16,340
You're a lawyer.

960
00:35:16,340 --> 00:35:17,570
Why do you care about the outstanding payment?

961
00:35:19,060 --> 00:35:19,570
This...

962
00:35:19,820 --> 00:35:20,210
No.

963
00:35:20,340 --> 00:35:21,610
If we manage to collect the payment,

964
00:35:21,610 --> 00:35:23,060
the factory will earn a good profit.

965
00:35:23,060 --> 00:35:24,380
Then, I'll earn money too.

966
00:35:24,460 --> 00:35:25,460
Isn't that a win-win situation?

967
00:35:27,250 --> 00:35:29,090
You shouldn't sacrifice anything
just to earn money.

968
00:35:29,820 --> 00:35:30,980
I didn't.

969
00:35:31,860 --> 00:35:32,820
I thought

970
00:35:32,940 --> 00:35:34,290
I could drop by and pay you a visit,

971
00:35:34,290 --> 00:35:35,730
while I bring you some businesses too.

972
00:35:36,980 --> 00:35:37,860
Think about it.

973
00:35:38,460 --> 00:35:39,770
I'm working for them.

974
00:35:40,020 --> 00:35:41,650
I can only do better if they do well.

975
00:35:43,060 --> 00:35:43,940
Am I right?

976
00:35:45,500 --> 00:35:46,690
Business is business, Xingfu.

977
00:35:46,900 --> 00:35:47,460
Can I book the rooms?

978
00:35:47,820 --> 00:35:48,650
There shouldn't be a problem, right?

979
00:35:49,060 --> 00:35:50,770
Of course. It's just a few rooms.

980
00:35:52,340 --> 00:35:53,170
I suppose this is good.

981
00:35:53,500 --> 00:35:55,210
If you manage to collect the debts,

982
00:35:55,420 --> 00:35:57,500
they will allocate a budget
to fix the roads to the inn too.

983
00:35:58,420 --> 00:35:59,460
Exactly.

984
00:35:59,980 --> 00:36:01,500
Now, it will benefit all three parties.

985
00:36:07,860 --> 00:36:08,820
Good morning, Xingfu.

986
00:36:09,290 --> 00:36:09,820
Morning.

987
00:36:10,540 --> 00:36:11,250
What's wrong?

988
00:36:11,250 --> 00:36:12,170
Did you not sleep well?

989
00:36:14,090 --> 00:36:14,730
Yes.

990
00:36:15,290 --> 00:36:16,020
Something's bothering me.

991
00:36:17,420 --> 00:36:18,690
Here's a piece of good news.

992
00:36:18,690 --> 00:36:19,730
I hope this can cheer you up.

993
00:36:20,090 --> 00:36:22,090
Our inn is fully booked for this coming weekend.

994
00:36:22,210 --> 00:36:22,820
What?

995
00:36:23,770 --> 00:36:25,250
All rooms have been reserved?

996
00:36:25,690 --> 00:36:26,210
