997
00:36:26,570 --> 00:36:27,730
Other than the rooms

998
00:36:27,730 --> 00:36:28,730
that are permanently rented

999
00:36:28,730 --> 00:36:30,540
to Madam Qi's husband and Mr. Wu,

1000
00:36:30,570 --> 00:36:31,820
all the other rooms have been reserved.

1001
00:36:32,130 --> 00:36:32,730
Really?

1002
00:36:34,460 --> 00:36:35,290
Are they all booked

1003
00:36:35,460 --> 00:36:36,690
by our acquaintances?

1004
00:36:36,690 --> 00:36:37,420
No.

1005
00:36:37,420 --> 00:36:38,860
They booked the rooms through phone calls.

1006
00:36:38,940 --> 00:36:40,650
They claimed to be Mr. Wu's fans,

1007
00:36:40,650 --> 00:36:42,690
wishing to pay our place a visit
after reading his Weibo.

1008
00:36:43,130 --> 00:36:44,090
Weibo?

1009
00:36:44,650 --> 00:36:45,340
You've read it?

1010
00:36:45,540 --> 00:36:46,130
I have.

1011
00:36:46,170 --> 00:36:46,900
Look at this.

1012
00:36:47,130 --> 00:36:47,770
This is the one.

1013
00:36:48,940 --> 00:36:51,650
He talked
about the water quality assessment incident

1014
00:36:51,980 --> 00:36:53,420
and his personal experience with this place.

1015
00:36:54,210 --> 00:36:54,900
Look.

1016
00:36:55,020 --> 00:36:56,250
He uploaded many photos too.

1017
00:36:58,690 --> 00:36:59,770
These photos look really nice.

1018
00:37:00,500 --> 00:37:02,420
He makes it sound
as if this is where the fairy lives.

1019
00:37:03,250 --> 00:37:03,570
Wow.

1020
00:37:03,570 --> 00:37:04,570
There are so many comments.

1021
00:37:06,290 --> 00:37:07,650
Our place is going to be really famous soon.

1022
00:37:08,130 --> 00:37:08,650
That's right.

1023
00:37:09,980 --> 00:37:10,380
Let's go.

1024
00:37:10,690 --> 00:37:12,170
Let's send our gratitude to Mr. Wu.

1025
00:37:12,290 --> 00:37:12,770
Sure.

1026
00:37:15,380 --> 00:37:16,170
Mr. Wu.

1027
00:37:16,940 --> 00:37:17,730
Good news.

1028
00:37:17,940 --> 00:37:18,420
Sure.

1029
00:37:18,500 --> 00:37:20,570
Our place has been fully booked
for the coming weekend.

1030
00:37:21,060 --> 00:37:22,730
All thanks to the post you uploaded on Weibo.

1031
00:37:22,940 --> 00:37:23,380
Really?

1032
00:37:23,380 --> 00:37:24,420
Many guests claimed

1033
00:37:24,650 --> 00:37:26,090
that they want to pay this place a visit

1034
00:37:26,090 --> 00:37:27,460
after reading that article.

1035
00:37:27,820 --> 00:37:28,980
I'm indebted to you.

1036
00:37:29,770 --> 00:37:30,540
You have no idea

1037
00:37:30,540 --> 00:37:32,610
how worried I was when the business was slow.

1038
00:37:32,900 --> 00:37:34,380
I wrote the article

1039
00:37:34,770 --> 00:37:36,980
because I wanted your inn to keep operating.

1040
00:37:37,250 --> 00:37:38,020
Where should I live

1041
00:37:38,250 --> 00:37:40,610
