1094
00:39:39,650 --> 00:39:40,770
Can I have your ID cards?

1095
00:39:40,900 --> 00:39:42,020
-They're with me.
-Please register here.

1096
00:39:44,130 --> 00:39:44,540
Xingfu.

1097
00:39:53,940 --> 00:39:55,820
This is the test report
of the water quality assessment

1098
00:39:55,820 --> 00:39:57,090
done by the Ministry of Ecology and Environment.

1099
00:40:06,170 --> 00:40:07,820
Mr. Xie, it's your first time here, right?

1100
00:40:08,020 --> 00:40:09,090
How do you feel about this place?

1101
00:40:12,940 --> 00:40:14,090
This is an article written by Mr. Wu

1102
00:40:14,420 --> 00:40:16,460
