1103
00:40:17,460 --> 00:40:19,380
He compliments the water here
for its superior quality.

1104
00:40:25,500 --> 00:40:26,170
Xingfu, we're all done.

1105
00:40:26,860 --> 00:40:27,420
Sure.

1106
00:40:27,690 --> 00:40:28,860
Mr. Xie, it's done.

1107
00:40:28,940 --> 00:40:29,980
Give me the room key.

1108
00:40:30,210 --> 00:40:30,980
I'll lead the way.

1109
00:40:30,980 --> 00:40:31,420
Xingfu.

1110
00:40:32,820 --> 00:40:33,730
I'll come with you.

1111
00:40:36,020 --> 00:40:36,940
Mr. Xie, this way, please.

1112
00:40:41,860 --> 00:40:42,980
